room_title: Escape room "Nana's Condo" by Escape House in Overland Park
review: Nana's Condo was a fun experience for both kids and adults! I highly recommend this one if you have younger kids in your group.

room_title: Escape room "Nana's Condo" by Escape House in Overland Park
review: Highly recommend! Nana's Condo was a blast. Great clues and props. No, we didn't make it out, but we were close and staff was very helpful with clues and throughout the entire experience. Fun day with a bunch of teenage boys.
